---
const title = "Mission Statement | Stangroom UK";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b0c10;
        --text: #eaeaf0;
        --muted: #9aa0a6;

        --accent1: #7c5cff;
        --accent2: #00d4ff;
        --accent3: #ff4ecd;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      /* NAVBAR */
      nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        z-index: 1000;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        opacity: 0.85;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 1; }

      .dropdown { position: relative; }

      .dropdown-content {
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        display: none;
        min-width: 200px;
      }

      .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content { display: block; }

      .dropdown::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 10px;
      }

      .dropdown-content a {
        display: block;
        padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      }

      /* BLOBS */
      .blob {
        position: fixed;
        width: 500px;
        height: 500px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(120px);
        opacity: 0.3;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      .blob.one { background: var(--accent1); top: -100px; left: -100px; }
      .blob.two { background: var(--accent2); bottom: -150px; right: -100px; }
      .blob.three { background: var(--accent3); top: 50%; left: 60%; }

      main {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        padding-top: 70px;
      }

      section {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 6rem 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .divider {
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent1), var(--accent2), var(--accent3));
      }

      p {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        text-align: center;
      }

      footer p { color: var(--muted); }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="blob one"></div>
    <div class="blob two"></div>
    <div class="blob three"></div>

    <!-- NAVBAR -->
    <nav>
      <div></div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <div class="dropdown">
          <a href="#">Services</a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="/sectors">Explore by sector</a>
            <a href="/indev">Explore by discipline</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/illuminating-futures">Illuminating Futures</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main>

      <section>
        <h1>Mission Statement</h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p>
          Stangroom UK exists to deliver reliable, high-quality technical services across live events, film, and broadcast. The focus is on practical execution, strong collaboration, and ensuring that every production runs safely and efficiently.
        </p>

        <p>
          By working across lighting, power, and systems, the aim is to provide a joined-up approach that supports both creative intent and technical requirements. This allows productions to operate smoothly, with clear communication between departments and dependable infrastructure on site.
        </p>

        <p>
          Alongside technical delivery, there is a strong commitment to supporting the next generation of industry professionals. Through real-world experience and access to live environments, emerging talent can gain meaningful insight into how productions operate.
        </p>

        <p>
          The goal is simple: deliver work that is dependable, professional, and forward-looking, while contributing positively to the wider industry.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- FOOTER -->
      <footer>
        <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <h3>Contact</h3>
          <p>
            Email: enquiries@stangroom.uk<br />
            Phone: +44 (0)1483 342 447<br />
            Based in the UK — available for live events, film & broadcast
          </p>

          <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <h3>Quick Links</h3>
            <p>
              <a href="/mission-statement">Mission Statement</a><br />
              <a href="/reports-policies">Reports, certifications and policies</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>
